### Column API Smoke Tests
### Run against local development environment

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@projectId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@columnId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@actorId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003

### List columns - requires auth
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}

### List columns - no auth returns 401/403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns

### Create column
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "In Progress",
    "color": "#FF0000",
    "wipLimit": 5
}

### Get column by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns/{{columnId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}

### Update column
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns/{{columnId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "In Review",
    "color": "#00FF00",
    "wipLimit": 3
}

### Reorder columns - valid IDs
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "columnIds": [
        "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
        "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
        "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005"
    ]
}

### Reorder columns - invalid ID returns 400
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "columnIds": [
        "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
        "99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999"
    ]
}

### Delete empty column
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns/{{columnId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}

### Delete non-empty column returns 409
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{projectId}}/columns/{{columnId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{actorId}}